# Native std.http JDK server host

[route, serveAsync, stop, httpGet, Response](std/http.ssc)

```scalascript
val port = args(0)
route("GET", "/ping") { req => Response.text("pong:" + req.path, 203) }
serveAsync(port)
println(httpGet("http://127.0.0.1:" + port + "/ping").status)
println(httpGet("http://127.0.0.1:" + port + "/ping").body)
stop()
```
